{
  "stem": "13556.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I've gone, like the railway station, [NON-ENGLISH], I've gone over there to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, welding.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now they did the same thing with me over there, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After I didn't even finish the year, they let me go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They call this [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They don't want me to have, like, a steady job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very much disappointed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I became pessimistic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- when you know you're capable to something else, and you have no opportunity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my family in Israel, they're very honest people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And honest people didn't have it-- money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They make a nice, balebatish, comfortable living in Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, to help me financially, nobody was prepared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they wish they could, as people with a good heart, they could help me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was disappointed with myself alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I didn't ask for nobody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have financial opportunity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I try in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- my, my-- in my head came different kind of fantasies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I tried to open up a new business in Israel-- coffee, coffee, to make coffee different taste, which we have it right now, called different name, different kind of coffee, and coffee to sell direct to the wholesales, groceries, not to have to do it individuals, the manufacturing.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You need money to start it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I couldn't find nobody to help me, to go in partnership.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I see it's a country, which without opportunity, and financial opportunity, you're nothing, especially when you're older.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they laid me off after 11 months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was very disappointed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was trying my best to, to work good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I figured up they, they will hold me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And still they didn't hold me.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
